  • 方法详细资料

    • initialize

      public void initialize()
      Initializes the controller after the FXML file has been loaded. This method is automatically called by the JavaFX framework. It prints the value of the 'ID' variable and calls the 'updateLearningTopicText()' and 'updatePersonInfoText()' methods. The 'ID' variable represents the identifier of the controller.

    • getInfoFromCsvByID

      public Info getInfoFromCsvByID()
      Retrieves a specific student information based on the ID.
      返回:
      the student information object matching the ID, or null if no match is found.

    • updatePersonInfoText

      public void updatePersonInfoText()
      Updates the person information text fields with the student's information. It retrieves the student's information using the getInfoFromCsvByID() method and updates the relevant text fields. If the student's information is available, it sets the text fields with the corresponding values. If the student's information is not available, the text fields remain unchanged.

    • updateLearningTopicText

      public void updateLearningTopicText()
      Updates the learning topic text field with the number of grades. It reads the grades from the "CourseScore.csv" file using the CSVtoList() method and counts the number of grades. It then sets the learning topic text field with the count of grades.

    • openWeb

      public void openWeb(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
      Opens a web page based on the source of the action event. If the source is the "toEmail" button, it opens the QMUL email login page. If the source is any other button, it opens the Google Scholar page.
      参数:
      actionEvent - the action event triggered by the user's click on a button.
